Craving for some comfort food? 
You can now enjoy a spread of grilled Peranakan flavours in the comfort of your own home! That’s right, @violetoonsingapore new grill menu really got me salivating for more! I really enjoyed the VO Street Satay, the meat is absolutely tender, and please don’t get me started on the Roti Violet, absolutely yummy! 
Swipe ⬅️ for full menu 📍Violet Oon Singapore
📧 eat@violetoon.com
